(14, 'Motorola Moto E XT1021', 'Motorola_Moto_E_XT1021', '6fPMBn5F', '<h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; ">Overview of Moto E</h2><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "></p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">The Motorola Moto E is a compact but strong performing smartphone with the sharpest display in its class.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Featuring Corning Gorilla Glass protection and a water-resistant splash guard, the Moto E has been designed to be durable and priced for all, not to mention all a battery life that will last all day.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Evolving from the Moto G, the E has a 1980mAh battery that offers fantastic battery life and performance considering the size and specification of the phone. Capable of lasting a working day for the average user, the Moto E does not lack on power and features.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">A 4.3” touchscreen display with 256PPI gives a superb viewing experience for images and video captured using the 5 megapixel camera or content your have downloaded onto the internal 4GB of memory.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">If you like to carry media or work with you then the microSD memory card slot makes it simple to store the additional memory hungry files and ensure you can continue to be productive, whatever it is you use the device for.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Protected by Corning Gorilla Glass 3, the touchscreen will absorb the odd knock and is considerably more resistant to scratching that most other phone screens.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">The additional benefit of the water-resistant coating will mean that should you spill something on your phone or get caught in the rain your device will survive.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Running the ever more powerful Android 4.4 operating system the Moto E is incredibly powerful out of the box.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">Pre-installed is the Google suite of applications to aid your communication and productivity needs. However full access to Google Play store means that you can easily access and download your favourite apps to enhance and personalise your user experience.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ">The built in 5 megapixel camera allows you to capture still images, video ad well as panoramic shots when required. Use the WiFi or 3G connection to share the images on your favourite social networks or use Bluetooth to share the file with other devices.</p><p styl