(39, 'Sony Smart Watch', 'Sony_Smart_Watch', 'SOkLlJo8', '<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px;">Sony SmartWatch 3 Overview</h2><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;"></p><p></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Building on past experiences Sony have developed the SmartWatch 3 to be the smartest of all the SmartWatches.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Equipped with Android Wear, Sony has evolved from their custom OS to bring them on par with the likes of Samsung, LG and Motorola.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">However Sony has set out to make their SmartWatch 3 the best for several reasons.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">A relatively new product, SmartWatches have a place, but research suggests that more than 50% still wish for a smartwatch to log their fitness and activities. As such the SmartWatch 3 boasts Sony’s Lifelogging technology that works in conjunction with your Android smartphone to keep track of you daily, weekly and monthly activity. From steps to calories it is all recorded.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">The watch itself has its own built in GPS chip, accelerometer and 4GB of internal storage designed for storing music on the wrist and not on the phone. Connect a set of Bluetooth headphones to the watch and you can stream that audio too them and control it all from your wrist. No need for a smartphone to be involved.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">IP68 rated, the watch will withstand immersion in water and can be worn all day with little in the way of limitation. Even wear it in the shower if you like.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">A stainless steel core ensures longevity and rigidity, whilst the different colour band options (sold spereately) ensure you have the most suitable design for you. The straps can not be interchanged like some other Android Wear products.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p><div class="productpanes" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="bodytext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 10px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.5;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Interact with the 1.6” touchscreen display or of course use the ‘Ok, Google’ command to give voice prompts to your wrist. Using the internet connection on your paired smartphone you can get key information right on your wrist.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">The Android Wear software is incredibly powerful and thanks to an extending portfolio of applications in the Google Play Store, right from your wrist you can get all of your notifications from various apps, respond to text messages and emails, play music, track your run, use a calculator or even remotely operate your smartphones camera.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">The built in 1.2Ghz processor should keep things running smoothly whilst the 420mAh battery should allow for up to 2 days usage.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">If you are always on the go, always looking to your phone for notifications and wishing to track your fitness then the SmartWatch 3 could save you time and effort and also make you more productive.</p><h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px;">Reasons to Buy Sony SmartWatch 3</h3><ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;"><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">1.6” transflective display</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Pixels 320x320</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">With voice, touch and gesture input</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Microphone</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Accelerometer, compass and gyro</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Google maps</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Bluetooth 4.0</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">BLE</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Waterproof IP68</li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p><h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px;">Sony SmartWatch 3 Box Contents</h3><ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;"><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">1 wrist strap</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Core unit (removable)</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">USB cable</li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); list-style-type: square; line-height: 1.2;">Quick startup guide</li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p><h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px;">Technical Specification of Sony SmartWatch 3</h3><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Weight<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">45g (core unit)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Display<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">1.6” transflective display<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">320 x 320 pixels</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Housing<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Stainless Steel</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Waterproof<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">IP68</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Performance/Capcity<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Quad ARM A7, 1.2GHz<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">512MB RAM, 4GB eMMC</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Controls<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Voice, touch and gesture input<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Microphone<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">On/off/wakeup button</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Battery<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">420mAh battery<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">2 days usage</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Sensors<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Ambient light sensor<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Accelerometer<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Compass and gyro<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">GPS<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">BLE</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Connectors<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Bluetooth 4.0<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">NFC<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">MicroUSB connector</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Variants<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">Stainless steel core – Wrist straps in various colours (sold separately)</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;">Compatibility<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">SmartWatch 3 is optimised for devices running on Android 4.3 and later.</p><div><br></div><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5;"></p></div></div><div class="titleBlock" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; position: relative; line-height: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></div>', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 188, 189, 0, 0, 737, 48, 6900, 9800, 2900, 29.5918, 0, 5, 150, 2, 0, 1411543800, 1419964200, 1419964200, 1411543183, 14, 1, 1, 15, 0);
