(3, 'HP 1000-1401AU Laptop', 'HP_1000-1401AU_Laptop', 'IJLylEW3', '<h3></h3><h2> HP 1000-1401AU Laptop (AMD Dual-core APU Processor E1-1500- 2GB RAM- 500GB HDD- 14.0Inch HD Display- Windows 8- AMD Radeon HD 7310 Graphics) (Glossy Imprint Black Licorice Colour)<label class="lang prod-desc-lang" style="cursor: inherit !important;"></label></h2><div class="details-content" style="font-size: 13px !important; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240) !important; "><p style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "><span lang="EN-GB">The <b>HP 1000-1401AU Laptop</b> has the power to handle almost any task you throw at it; thanks to its raucous power, state-of-the-art technologies and stylish design. This 14.0-inch laptop packed with a powerful AMD Dual-core APU Processor E1-1500, 2GB of RAM, AMD Radeon HD 7310 graphics and a 500GB hard drive space is certainly a wise buy.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "><span lang="EN-GB">It features a <b>14.0-inch LED screen</b> that lets you enjoy vivid images and videos without straining your eyes. The <b>backlit widescreen</b> has a <b>resolution of 1366X768 HD</b> which ensures sharper pictures and more vibrant colours. Also, it has <b>16:9 true wide aspect ratio</b> to prevent images and videos from getting pixelated.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "><span lang="EN-GB">Multi-tasking is never a problem as the laptop comes equipped with <b>2GB of DDR3 RAM</b>. To further ensure that you can carry your world in this compact laptop, it sports <b>500 GB of hard drive space</b>. From documents to movies to space consuming software, you can save chunks of data in <b>HP 1000-1401AU</b>. It is powered by <b>AMD E1 Series APU Processor E1-1500 (Dual Core) processor</b> with a <b>clock speed of 1.48 GHz</b> and <b>1 MB L2 cache memory</b>, which make sure you enjoy fast and efficient performance. The laptop is loaded with <b>Windows 8 </b>operating system that promises a plethora of applications that are entertaining, interesting and engaging.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "><span lang="EN-GB">Striking a perfect balance between work and entertainment, the <b>HP 1000-1401AU </b>is equipped with<b> Altec Lansing stereo speakers. </b>In addition, it sports<b> HP TrueVision HD webcam </b>having a resolution of 1280X720 by 24 frames and a<b> single digital microphone. </b>To satiate the needs of gaming buffs, it features<b> AMD Radeon HD 7310 graphics.</b></span></p><p style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; ">To ensure smooth connectivity and communication, the versatile laptop features integrated <b>Bluetooth 4.0 +HS</b>, one HDMI, one VGA Out, <b>three USB 2.0 ports</b> and a Kensington lock slot. Its <b>6 cell Lithium Ion battery</b> keeps the laptop charged so that it carries out all desired tasks incessantly. Other key features you may enjoy with the purchase of this HP laptop include full-size textured pocket keyboard, touchpad with multi-touch gesture support and many moreâ€¦</span></p><p style="padding: 0px 8px; line-height: 20px !important; color: rgb(46, 46, 46) !important; font-family: tahoma !important; "></p></div><a href="http://www.snapdeal.com/product/hp-10001401au-laptop-amd-dualcore/1610074509#top" class="back-to-top" style="color: rgb(15, 45, 94); text-de