 rgb(255, 255, 255); ">This <b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; ">Forbes Trendy Vacuum Cleaner has a power requirement of 230 V</b> and is powered through electrical wire that has to be plugged into a wall power socket. The Nano Vacuum cleaner from Eureka Forbes is a <b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; ">dry dust collector</b>and uses a filter bag to separate the dust from the air being pulled in.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 2px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-family: arial, tahoma, verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: left; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; ">Body And Design</b></p><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, tahoma, verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: left; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">The </span><b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: arial, tahoma, verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: left; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Forbes Trendy Nano Vacuum Cleaner has a well-designed compact body</b><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, tahoma, verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: left; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "> which manages to have enough on-board storage space for its cleaning accessories. The </span><b style="margin: 0px; paddin